        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>A tool to mix two images into a schematic file for Minecraft. Featuring the base colors of <code>crimson_stem</code> and <code>warped_stem</code> with their stripped variants, what players see is one image, while the map shows the other.</p>
<p>The tool is built by Gemini and is open source and available on <a href="https://github.com/Lylighte/feature-mapart">GitHub</a>.</p>
<p><img src="https://www.lylighte.cc/file/p/static/2026/02/feature-mapart.jpg?sign=fws0wlFPzSNZrgFbV_HGaokLOlx92ZJ4MLbP_DfznAM=:0" alt="" /></p>
]]></content>
